estenh: Added component.json for bower

Fixing bug with extracting hyphenated urls from domains without protocol

twttr.txt.extractUrls failed to extract the full url if the url
contained hyphens if the url was lacking a protocol.
E.g.:
message with http://www.hyphen-url.com -> http://www.hyphen-url.com
message with www.hyphen-url.com -> url.com
message with hyphen-url.com -> url.com

This patch adds the hyphen to the validAsciiDomain regex, and also adds
a couple simple tests to cover this scenario.
